-   **[VSD Overview](overview.html)**

    VSD helps you monitor the performance of <%=vars.product_name%> and diagnose performance problems.

-   **[Installing and Running VSD](running_vsd.html)**

    Start the VSD tool, load statistics files, and maintain the view you want on your statistics.

-   **[Viewing Statistics in VSD](viewing_stats_in_vsd.html)**

    Select statistics and view them using chart templates and customized charts.

